    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/186">Sicardus</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, motus
                        Dei omnipotentis misericordia, pro redemptione anime nostre seu gentis et
                        patrie, suggerente potestatis nostre <rs key="#Personal_rank">viro
                            venerabile</rs>
                        <persName key="#Prevosts" ref="#people/192">Bassaci</persName>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts">preposito</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Landed_possessions #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/85"
                                ><rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> Sancte Sophie</orgName> sito
                        infra hanc Beneventanam civitatem nostram, <rs key="#Intercessory">per
                            rogum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/1905"
                            >Roffrid</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">referendarii</rs> nostri, concedimus in
                        prephato Beate Sophie cenobio <rs
                            key="#Fisheries #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >piscatione</rs> in mare <placeName key="#Cities #Fiscal_property"
                            ref="#places/2836">Sipontina</placeName> per hos vero <rs key="#Fines"
                            >fines</rs> et mensuras, hoc est passus ducenti ex una parte fine <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">piscatione</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1913">Sancte Marie
                            Beneventane ecclesie</orgName>, sed et de alia parte fine <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">piscatione</rs> que nostre reservavimus potestatem, et
                        da terra firma fine <placeName key="#Rivers" ref="#places/3459"
                            >Salzola</placeName>, in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per
                        hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum supra nominato cenobio eiusque rectores
                        integra supradicta piscatione per iam dictos fines et mensuras habere et
                        possidere seu dominare atque piscare valeatis et a nullo ex nostris
                        iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldis vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeatis
                        aliquam requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod vero
                        preceptus concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Writer" ref="#people/3462">Theodericus</persName>. Actus
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/110">Beneventus</placeName>
                        secundo anno, mense apreli, tertia decima indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
